    <h1 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-10">Why flight free?</h1>
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">Reducing our carbon emissions is vital in avoiding climate breakdown. There are lots of things we can do, like eating less meat, using renewable energy, and driving less. But did you know that just one flight can wipe out all your savings?</p>
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-16 leading-tight">Taking a flight free year is a great way to cut your emissions and give other ways of travelling a try.</p>

