        <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">Not everybody flies, but for those that do, flights are likely to make up the biggest chunk of your carbon footprint. It's one of the most high-carbon ways of travelling, so switching to another mode of transport can make a huge impact on our emissions.</p>
        <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-16 leading-tight">Find out how much of your carbon footprint is taken up by flights with the <a href="https://footprint.wwf.org.uk/" target="_blank" class="border-b-2 border-orange hover:text-orange">WWF carbon footprint calculator</a>.</p>

