<section class="section--social_change bg-orange text-blue-dark">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-8 xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pt-12 pb-12">
    <h2 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-10">To inspire social change</h2>
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">It might seem that flying is normal, especially if lots of people around you fly. We are strongly influenced by what others do, and as more people choose to stop flying, more will follow.</p>
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">Our aim is to challenge the norm when it comes to flying, and shift the narrative away from taking flights as the default. When lots of people take action together, that's when real change happens.</p>

